title: Jasmine Crockett called Texas Senate race contenders as she weighs jumping into fray
description: As intrigue grows over whether Texas Democratic Rep. Jasmine Crockett plans to announce a U.S. Senate campaign next week, she confirmed to CBS News she's spoken with would-be opponents.
